venum kvanantamaravindadalayataksam
barhavatam samasitambuda-sundarangam
kandarpa-koti-kamaniya vishesha-shobham
govindam adi-purusham tam aham bhajami

ānando brahmeti vyajānāt 
ānandādhyeva khalvimāni bhūtāni jāyante 
ānandena jātāni jīvanti 
ānandaṃ prayantyabhisaṃviśantīti 

yo’ntaḥpraviśya mama vācamimāṃ prasuptāṃ
sañjīvayatyakhila-śaktidhara: svadhāmnā ।
anyāṃśca hasta-caraṇa-śravaṇa-tvagādīn-
prāṇān namo bhagavate puruṣāya tubhyam ॥


shrnvantu visve amrtasya putra 
aa ye dhaamaani divyaani tasthuH

dharmasetu paalakam tvadharmamarga naashakam
karmapasha mochakam susharma daayakam vibhum
svarna varna keshapaasha shobhitanga mandalam
kaashikaapuradhinaath kaalabhairavam bhaje

vedo'khiladharmamoolam

vedo nityamadheeyataam


